sentence: The war cry for justice was all over - Much to the chagrin of the authorities.
Lao: ການຮ້ອງໄຫ້ສົງຄາມເພື່ອຄວາມຍຸຕິທໍາແມ່ນຫມົດທຸກຢ່າງ - ຫຼາຍຕໍ່ກັບເຈົ້າຫນ້າທີ່.
backtrans: Crying war for justice is all-more with the authorities.

sentence: The regime's decision adumbrates the underlying agenda.
Lao: ການຕັດສິນໃຈຂອງລະບອບໄດ້ຮັບການຕັດສິນການວາລະການພົວພັນລະບອບລະບອບ.
backtrans: Decisions of the regime has been judged by the regulator of the regime.

sentence: The community was anxious over the passing of the much needed reforms.
Lao: ຊຸມຊົນມີຄວາມກັງວົນໃຈໃນການຖ່າຍທອດການປະຕິຮູບທີ່ຈໍາເປັນຫຼາຍ.
backtrans: Communities are concerned in passing many necessary reforms.

sentence: The think tank  published a paper outlining their apology of capital punishment.
Lao: ຖັງຄິດທີ່ເຜີຍແຜ່ເອກະສານທີ່ຊີ້ໃຫ້ເຫັນການຂໍໂທດຂອງເຂົາເຈົ້າກ່ຽວກັບການລົງໂທດນະຄອນຫຼວງ.
backtrans: The tank is aware of the document that indicates their apology on capital punishment.

sentence: Aught was left of the petition's validity
Lao: ughted ແມ່ນປະໄວ້ຂອງຄວາມຖືກຕ້ອງຂອງການຮ້ອງຟ້ອງຂອງ
backtrans: utted is left of the accuracy of the petition

sentence: The President exhorted his ministers to buckle up as key opposition support for his economic plan was about to buckle.
Lao: ປະທານາທິບໍດີໄດ້ແນະນໍາລັດຖະມົນຕີຂອງລາວໃຫ້ເປັນຜູ້ສະຫນັບສະຫນູນການຄັດຄ້ານດ້ານເສດຖະກິດຂອງທ່ານແມ່ນກໍາລັງຈະຄຸເຂົ່າ.
backtrans: The President suggested his ministers to support your economic opposition is to kneel.

sentence: The voters were chuffed to see the bill passed.
Lao: ຜູ້ມີສິດເລືອກຕັ້ງໄດ້ຮັບການສົນທະນາເພື່ອເບິ່ງວ່າໃບບິນຜ່ານຜ່ານໄປ.
backtrans: The optist has been talking to see if the bill has gone.

sentence: The lawyer's discursive narration swayed the jury.
Lao: ການເລົ່າເລື່ອງການປະກາດຂອງທະນາຍຄວາມຂອງທະນາຍຄວາມໄດ້ເຮັດໃຫ້ຄະນະກໍາມະການ.
backtrans: The proclamation of the lawyer declaration of lawyers made the commission.

Lao: ສານສານໄດ້ເຂົ້າຮ່ວມຄວາມຮຸນແຮງ!

sentence: The EU block opposed an eventual imposition of anti-dumping measures.
Lao: ສະຫນາມສະຫະພາບເອີຣົບຄັດຄ້ານການບັງຄັບໃຫ້ເກີດການປ້ອງກັນມາດຕະການຕ້ານການຖອກນ້ໍາ.
backtrans: The European Union opposes the force of protection against the anti-watering measures.

sentence: A fulsome eulogy was delivered by the sly counsel.
Lao: elogy ທີ່ບໍ່ສົມບູນໄດ້ຖືກປົດປ່ອຍໂດຍຄໍາແນະນໍາຂອງ SLY.
backtrans: Annology is not completely delivered by the instructions sly.

sentence: The gig-economy agency decided to garnish the refunds!
Lao: ອົງການຂອງເສດຖະກິດ Gig- ໄດ້ຕັດສິນໃຈແຕ່ງເງິນຄືນ!
backtrans: GIG-economic agency decided to make money back!

sentence: Members of the anti-theocratic revolutionary movement overthrew the peers in power!
Lao: ສະມາຊິກຂອງການເຄື່ອນໄຫວປະຕິວັດປະຕິວັດຕໍ່ຕ້ານການປະຕິເສດໄດ້ໂຄ່ນລົ້ມເພື່ອນຮ່ວມງານໃນອໍານາດ!
backtrans: A member of the revolutionary revolutionary movement against the rejection to overthrow their colleagues!

sentence: The traitors disappointingly decided to fight with the colonialists.
Lao: ຜູ້ທໍລະຍົດທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບການຕັດສິນໃຈທີ່ຈະຕໍ່ສູ້ກັບອານານິຄົມ.
backtrans: The traitor that was decided to fight the colonies.
